      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This car is the perfect find for a mechanical enthusiast looking for a rewarding challenge. While it currently requires some significant TLC and mechanical attention to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone who loves to restore and revive. It's an affordable way to get your hands on a vehicle with tons of potential!",
